               <milestone n="1" unit="line"/> [...] already and [...] (something) else. If you are neglectful, you will be sure to be in trouble. Greetings, Year [...]. 
<milestone n="4" rend="break" unit="line"/> Theodoros to Diotimos, greetings. Please write urgently to Androsthenes and the nomarchs to send the anouchi using all the draught-animals, just as they did before. 
<milestone n="7" unit="line"/> With the river rising higher up to all the dykes, everything has to be strengthened. (Tell him also) to send the [...].
<note>Translation with slight modifications: B. Van Beek in P.Petr.Kleon, p. 95, © Peeters</note>
